Package PIM

Interface PIMPackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
PIMPackage
public static interface PIMPackage.Literals
Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each operation of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
